title: 2021 Life Science XP Education Symposium
description: The Biocom Institute Education Symposium invites K-12 educators, nonprofits and industry partners who are reimagining Life Science/Biotech learning experiences in their classrooms, schools and districts. Participants will engage in a variety of professional learning and networking opportunities to connect with innovative educators and industry experts & scientists, such as the leaders of Berkeley companies, Bayer and Caribou Biosciences.
